query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND t.title not like '%road%' AND t.title not like '%tree%' AND t.title not like '%camera%' AND t.title not like '%ice%' AND t.production_year > 2005 AND t.production_year < 2006 AND cn.country_code in ('ke','bn','tf','sg','gt') AND cn.name not like '%Pixar Animation Studios%' AND cn.name not like '%Blumhouse Productions%' AND cct1.kind in ('complete+verified','complete','cast') AND mi.info in ('Zulu','Portuguese','Afrikaans','Flemish','Georgian','Mandarin','Ladino','Spanish','Norwegian','Maori','Kalmyk-Oirat','Bulgarian','German') AND (chn.name like '%Doctor Strange%' OR chn.name like '%Luke Skywalker%' OR chn.name like '%Harley Quinn%') AND n.gender in ('f') AND (n.name like '%U%' OR n.name like '%l%' OR n.name like '%C%' OR n.name like '%v%') AND (k.keyword like '%paranormal%') AND it.info in ('top 250 rank','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','birth notes','LD additional information','LD picture format','LD frequency response','certificates','tech info','LD certification','LD audio noise','LD year','LD sharpness','locations','LD video standard') AND cct2.kind in ('complete+verified','cast','complete') AND it3.info in ('LD release country','rating','interviews','LD disc format','LD color information','agent address') AND pi.note not like '%Galan Inc. Television/Film%' AND pi.note not like '%Jillian Thomas%' AND (an.name like '%P%') AND (mc.note like '%Portugal%' OR mc.note like '%Canada%')
